      "x": -60,
      "y": -60,
      "width": 900,
      "height": 200,
      "label": "📥 Inputs (from upstream pipelines)"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2-input",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "**A2 — Entity Extraction** (6:30 AM)\nNews → Sonnet 4.6 → entities\n→ `topic_clusters` + `keywords` tables"
    },
    {
      "id": "h-input",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "**H — GSC Export**\nGoogle Search Console → 7-day CSV\n→ `data/gsc-exports/latest.csv`"
    },

    {
      "id": "e-discovery",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 340,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## E — Cluster Discovery\n`planner.ts` · Manual/Cron\n\n**6-stage candidate discovery:**\n1. SERP Demand (Serper.dev · 7 queries)\n2. Exa Semantic Gap (findSimilar)\n3. Competitor Audit (Exa/Brave + LLM)\n4. News Signals (14-day scan + LLM)\n5. GSC Import (unmatched queries)\n6. Multi-signal Scoring (0–100)\n\n**Management:**\n`--promote=<slug>` · `--dismiss=<slug>`\n`--promote-above=<score>` · `--status`"
    },
    {
      "id": "j-strategy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 480,
      "y": 240,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## J — Weekly Strategy\n`generate-seo.ts --weekly-strategy`\n\nGap analysis: clusters × content\nBrave demand validation (top 10)\n→ `data/content-plan/{week}.json`"
    },

    {
      "id": "cluster-json",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 160,
      "y": 660,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "**flagship-clusters/{slug}.json**\nTargets (status: missing → exists)\nCandidates · Refresh flags"
    },

    {
      "id": "d-seo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 840,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## D — SEO Daily Generation\n`generate-seo.ts` · **9:00 AM SGT**\n\nGap: `topic_clusters` × content existence\nTop 10 clusters (mention_count ≥ 2)\nMax 8 pages/run · EN + ZH\n\n**Page types:**\n- Glossary (pillar topic entry)\n- FAQ (from brave-discussion / blog)\n- Compare (vs pattern / blog)\n- Topic Hub (mention ≥ 5)"
    },
    {
      "id": "f-cluster",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 840,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## F — Cluster Content Gen\n`generate-seo.ts --cluster=<SLUG>`\n\nLoad targets with status=missing\nSource resolution chain:\ncurated URL → Exa → Brave → empty\n\n**Generates:**\n- Cornerstone blog (2000–4000 tok)\n- Compare / FAQ / Glossary pages\n- Max 8 pages/run · EN + ZH\n→ Update cluster status"
    },

    {
      "id": "content-output",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -60,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 840,
      "height": 160,
      "label": "📄 Generated Content (→ Vercel)"
    },
    {
      "id": "out-glossary",
