    {
      "id": "g-refresh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 880,
      "y": 660,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## G — Refresh Engine\n\n**Detection** `--refresh-check`:\nFreshness signals → page mapping\nLLM staleness → severity flags\n(pricing-change · new-feature ·\ndeprecation · platform-change)\n\n**Execution** `--refresh`:\nRe-generate with fresh sources\nEN + ZH independently\nPreserves internal links"
    },
    {
      "id": "k-health",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 880,
      "y": 1000,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "0",
      "text": "## K1 — Cluster Health\n`cluster-health.ts`\n\nCompleteness (targets by type)\nLink health (broken/orphan/density)\nRefresh status · GSC performance\n→ `data/reports/cluster-health-*.md`"
    }
  ],
